-- US SEC adopts final rules on ABS registration and disclosure
-- By Douwe Miedema
-- Wed Aug 27, 2014 11:01AM EDT
-- None



WASHINGTON, Aug 27 (Reuters) - The U.S. Securities and Exchange Commission in a public vote on Wednesday unanimously adopted final rules on the registration and disclosure of asset-backed securities, which stood at the heart of the 2007-09 credit crisis. [ID:nL1N0QX10G]

